wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-old.png\" alt=\"keyy login previous cryptograph\" width=\"329\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-old.png 329w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-old-190x300.png 190w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" /></a></p>\n<p>And for those who didn’t know about Keyy, we placed a “what is this?” link, clicking on which loaded a text explanation of this login method.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-whats-this-old.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-229542 aligncenter\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-whats-this-old.png\" alt=\"keyy login what\'s this previous version\" width=\"330\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-whats-this-old.png 330w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/keyy-login-whats-this-old-183x300.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The <strong>new login cryptograph</strong> makes it much easier to switch to a QR code, thanks to a toggle that refreshes that portion quickly and seamlessly. Also, the toggle looks clearer, which makes the UX better.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.25.36-PM.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-229543 aligncenter\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.25.36-PM.png\" alt=\"Keyy login new cryptograph\" width=\"326\" height=\"443\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.25.36-PM.png 569w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.25.36-PM-221x300.png 221w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.25.36-PM-510x694.png 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 326px) 100vw, 326px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In addition, we changed the “what is this? With a “learn more” link, clicking on which the cryptograph fades and detailed installation instructions appear on the screen. This is meant to make it easier for users who don’t have Keyy set up to get up and running. Especially useful for admins who want all their website users to login with Keyy.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-229544 aligncenter\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM.png\" alt=\"Keyy login new set up instruction\" width=\"314\" height=\"406\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM.png 618w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM-232x300.png 232w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM-510x659.png 510w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM-610x789.png 610w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-12-at-6.33.27-PM-400x516.png 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 314px) 100vw, 314px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Thanks to your support and appreciation, <em><strong>Keyy has now over 900 active installs</strong></em>. We achieved this in only two months after first launch.</p>\n<p>Keep following our blog for further updates!</p>\n<span class=\"et_bloom_bottom_trigger\"></span><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/new-keyy-login-cryptograph/\">The new Keyy login cryptograph</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"comment