news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=228664\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:759:\"<p>Why Reduced Redundancy is not available for Amazon S3 Enhanced add on anymore? If you are an UpdraftPlus Premium user, you may have recently noticed that Reduced Redundancy is not available anymore for the Amazon S3 extension. The only two &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/aws-s3-reduced-redundancy-storage-being-phased-out/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/aws-s3-reduced-redundancy-storage-being-phased-out/\">AWS S3 Reduced Redundancy Storage being phased out</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Fabio Rossi\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3331:\"<p><b>Why Reduced Redundancy is not available for Amazon S3 Enhanced add on anymore?</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are an </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/shop/updraftplus-premium/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus Premium</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> user, you may have recently noticed that Reduced Redundancy is not available anymore for the Amazon S3 extension. The only two options in the Storage class drop-down list are </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Standard </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Standard (infrequent access)</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-228665\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-1024x685.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-1024x685.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-300x201.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-768x514.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-510x341.png 510w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-610x408.png 610w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes-1080x722.png 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/AmazonS3-Storage-classes.png 1256w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is not due to a bug in our plugin or to a configuration error. </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mysteriouscode.io/blog/aws-s3-storage-classes-pricing-is-not-what-you-think/#update1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reduced Redundancy is being phased out lately</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> by AWS and that is why we chose to remove this option from </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/shop/s3-enhanced/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus Premium &#8211; Amazon S3 add on</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> settings panel.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do not worry about the rest, though! All other <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/shop/s3-enhanced/\">functionalities of this premium add on</a> are active and, in general, the whole </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-1-13-6-free-version-2-13-6-paid-versions/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus code has been improved and enhanced</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> lately. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our aim remains to continuously improve our plugin, to make it more and more easy-to-use, performant and tailored on your ever-changing needs. </span></p>\n<span class=\"et_bloom_bottom_trigger\"></span><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/aws-s3-reduced-redundancy-storage-being-phased-out/\">AWS S3 Reduced Redundancy Storage being phased out</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://updraftplus.com/aws-s3-reduced-redundancy-storage-being-phased-out/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://updraftplus.com/aws-s3-reduced-redundancy-storage-being-phased-out/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n	