	(640,2,'2014-11-18 13:47:16','2014-11-18 13:47:16','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Consecutive second time Ludhiana based GEE7 has won the Scodix Design Awards in the Photo Web 2 Print category. The competition has received many entries submitted across six different categories. GEE7 is the only Indian winner among 12 award</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">PRLog - Nov. 18, 2014 - NEW DELHI, India -- Consecutive second time Ludhiana based GEE7 Printek has won the Scodix Design Awards in the Photo Web 2 Print category. The competition has received many entries submitted across six different categories.  GEE7 is the only Indian winner among 12 award winners in this award organized by Scodix, Israel.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a id=\"set-post-thumbnail\" class=\"thickbox\" title=\"Set featured image\" href=\"http://icv.dev/wp-admin/media-upload.php?post_id=640&amp;type=image&amp;TB_iframe=1\"><img class=\"attachment-266x266\" src=\"http://icv.dev/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/scodix-award-2014-300x146.jpg\" alt=\"scodix award 2014\" width=\"412\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vishal Luther, CEO, GEE7 said “We are truly and honestly thrilled after winning this award. This is the realization of huge life dream. As we have earlier said that Scodix is a machine for those who have creative ideas in their mind but were not able to implement them because of the limitations of technology. After the installation of Scodix we have gained a lot and it is easy for us to apply the ideas, we can do a lot of creative work with this now and the result is in front of all of us. Our sincerely thanks to the Scodix family who have organized this competition as it has motivated us to do something different from our regular work. It was a great challenge for us to think out of the box and create something unique. We are proud to be a part of Scodix family.”</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The successful launch last year of the Scodix Design Awards led to such excitement, customer and media interest that the Scodix was delighted to continue the same tradition this year. The 2014 contest for the best creative work produced by Scodix customers using Scodix SENSE™ Digital Print Enhancement technology yielded a record-breaking number of applications.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">75 Scodix users from all over the globe submitted their best work for an opportunity to demonstrate the premium quality differentiation they offer their clients, gain worldwide recognition of their work, as well as a chance to win the award.</p>','Scodix Design Awards 2014 goes to GEE7','','publish','open','open','','scodix-design-awards-2014-goes-to-gee7','','','2014-11-23 13:53:10','2014-11-23 13:53:10','',0,'http://icv.dev/?p=640',0,'post','',0),
