	(708,2,'2015-03-03 12:32:21','2015-03-03 12:32:21','The production speed and features of the innovative Scodix Ultra Pro Digital Enhancement Press are ideal for commercial print service providers, folding cartons packaging converters, and web-to-print shops.\r\n\r\nWASHINGTON DC – Scodix, the leading provider of digital enhancement solutions for the graphic arts industry, today announced they will be featuring the industry’s most versatile digital enhancement press at this week’s DSCOOPX. The conference will mark the first live demonstration of Scodix Ultra™ Pro at the Dscoop annual event. Scodix, a Platinum sponsor of this year’s event, will hand out samples of commercial and folding carton projects in what will be the company’s largest DSCOOP exhibit ever (booth #539).\r\n\r\nAnd on Thursday (March 5th at 1:45 pm), Scodix will conduct a special panel titled “Outstanding Sales with Scodix SENSE™” (DSCOOP Partner Sessions). At this session (in the Maryland 1 Room), Scodix customers will share their experience from implementing Scodix, and the reverberating effects it has had on their business. Users will also showcase their most profitable digital enhancement applications, and discuss how Scodix systems have driven new revenue streams and built bridges to whole new customer bases.','Scodix Ultra Pro Press to be Demonstrated Live at the 2015 DSCOOPX Annual Conference','','publish','open','open','','scodix-ultra-pro-press-to-be-demonstrated-live-at-the-2015-dscoopx-annual-conference','','','2015-03-04 12:41:09','2015-03-04 12:41:09','',0,'http://icv.dev/?p=708',0,'post','',0),
