under; Aaron Tartakovsky, cofounder of Epic CleanTec; Roy Wiesner, CEO of Hutchison Kinrot ; Lyuba Wolf of ChargePoint; and Glenn Yago, senior director of the Milken Innovation Center at the Jerusalem Institute for Israel Studies.</p>','Israel-Calif Green-Tech Partnership launches at Google','','inherit','closed','closed','','823-revision-v1','','','2015-10-25 14:35:07','2015-10-25 14:35:07','',823,'http://icv.dev/uncategorized/823-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
