	(974,2,'2016-05-04 12:26:43','2016-05-04 12:26:43','<em>Top analyst report identifies Freightos amongst 5 supply chain companies considered to be innovative, impactful and intriguing.</em>\r\n\r\nFreightos, the world’s online freight marketplace and provider of instant freight pricing technology, has been named a Cool Vendor by Gartner, a leading IT consulting firm, in the Cool Vendors in Supply Chain Services, 2016 report (1). The report recognizes five companies that help supply chain organizations improve operations with technology and specialized expertise.\r\n\r\nFreightos enables companies to streamline their supply chain by instantly generating international pricing and routing for global freight shipments, with live rate comparisons from the global Freightos Marketplace. Freightos customers include Fortune 100 companies, global logistics providers and mid-sized business.\r\n\r\n“We’re thrilled to be selected as a Gartner Cool Vendor,” said Freightos CEO Zvi Schreiber. “Gartner has played a fundamental role in improving supply chains globally. We believe that Freightos’ inclusion in the 2016 report is a testament to our role in bringing international freight online…and into the 21st century.”\r\n\r\nGartner subscribers can access the full Gartner report here. Explore how Freightos can reduce logistics costs and improve efficiency with online freight at freightos.com\r\n\r\nDisclaimer:\r\n\r\nGartner does not endorse any vendor, product or service depicted in our research publications, and does not advise technology users to select only those vendors with the highest ratings or other designation. Gartner research publications consist of the opinions of Gartner’s research organization and should not be construed as statements of fact. Gartner disclaims all warranties, expressed or implied, with respect to this research, including any warranties of merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose.\r\n\r\nAbout Freightos\r\n\r\nFreightos is automating the trillion dollar global freight industry. Freightos uses Big Data technology to enable forwarders, shippers and carriers to manage rates and automate freight routing, pricing and booking online, introducing unprecedented efficiency and transparency into the industry. Registered in Hong Kong with offices in the Middle East, Asia, Europe and the US, Freightos has already helped dozens of freight forwarders, including top ten global companies and Fortune 100 retailers, automate freight sales, routing and pricing online, and provide big data-drive business insights to optimize operations','Freightos named a 2016 Cool Vendor in Supply Chain Services','','publish','open','open','','freightos-named-a-2016-cool-vendor-in-supply-chain-services','','','2016-05-08 12:30:08','2016-05-08 12:30:08','',0,'http://icv.dev/?p=974',0,'post','',0),
