	(1196,2,'2017-02-01 08:17:22','2017-02-01 08:17:22','<div class=\"page-title\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-9 col-sm-push-3\">\r\n<div class=\"section-title\">\r\n<div class=\"has-border \">\r\n<h2>Avery Dennison offers print enhancements for branding</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<img class=\"attachment-266x266 \" src=\"http://icv.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/missy-franklin-768x334.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 266px) 100vw, 266px\" srcset=\"http://icv.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/missy-franklin-768x334.jpg 768w, http://icv.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/missy-franklin.jpg 960w\" alt=\"missy franklin\" width=\"562\" height=\"245\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"parbase text\">\r\n\r\nDive in! Avery Dennison RBIS is pleased to announce our recent collaboration with swimwear brand Speedo to create a hangtag featuring our Foil Sense by <a href=\"http://rbis.averydennison.com/en/home/our-solutions/solutions-scodix.html\">Scodix</a><sup>TM </sup>solution to support the launch of its <a title=\"missy\" href=\"http://www.speedostore.co.uk/inspiration/story/missy-franklin-usa\" target=\"_blank\">Missy Franklin</a> Signature Series collection. Foil Sense by Scodix<sup>TM </sup>is the latest in a range of Scodix print enhancement products RBIS <a title=\"Scodix\" href=\"http://rbis.averydennison.com/en/home/our-solutions/solutions-scodix.html\">offers</a>, creating flashy, eye-catching and shiny raised effects on labeling and branding materials.\r\n\r\nDesigned in collaboration with the five-time Olympic medalist and holder of two individual world records, the collection will be colorful, feminine and performance based, featuring a logo with an “M” in the shape of a heart. Scodix technology enhanced the color on the chosen signature tag, allowing it to \'pop\' with a special rainbow effect. The Sense solution produces an embossed effect by applying polymer to the graphic tag at varying heights. The result: a flashy heart with raised effects.\r\n\r\nScodix by nature provides more sustainable solutions and various environmental benefits, due to reduced setup and run time, decreased UV power usage, and reduced hazardous waste compared to traditional print processes.\r\n\r\nSpeedo chose Foil Sense by Scodix<sup>TM</sup> to drive the personality of the collection, both inspiring women and tapping into their passion for swimming. “We worked closely with Speedo and Scodix to test various sheets and treatments for the perfect look,\" said Rana Sidahmed, RBIS\' global creative director of Trends and Insights.\r\n\"This was all done with a quick turnaround thanks to the benefits of the sustainable digital printing technology.”\r\n\r\n“The collection is designed to make women and girls feel comfortable and confident in and out of the water, and we were happy to work with Avery Dennison RBIS to tell this story through the hangtag and carry it throughout the collection,” Masami Shigematsu, senior director, Softlines Product Development, Speedo, explained.\r\n\r\nTo celebrate <a title=\"Olympics\" href=\"http://www.teamusa.org/News/2016/August/21/Team-USA-Concludes-Record-Breaking-Rio-2016-Olympic-Games-With-121-Medals-46-Golds\" target=\"_blank\">Team USA’s success in the 2016 Olympics</a>, Speedo is set to release the <a title=\"Missy\" href=\"http://www.speedostore.co.uk/inspiration/story/missy-franklin-usa\" target=\"_blank\">Missy Franklin</a> Signature Series of performance suits for women and girls in early 2017 from <a title=\"Speedo\" href=\"http://speedousa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">speedousa.com</a>. According to Speedo, the Missy Franklin Signature Series will feature 18 pieces, including one-piece suits and mix-and-match separates across three vibrant color stories.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"parbase text\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Speedo Empowers Female Athletes, with a New Look from RBIS','','inherit','closed','closed','','1194-revision-v1','','','2017-02-01 08:17:22','2017-02-01 08:17:22','',1194,'http: